Date: Fri, 25 Jul 2025 12:45:22 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL hostapd: Implement CLI to validate afc
 trigger

Implement hostapd cli to validate afc trigger by compare eirp

command: hostapd_cli -i wlanx afc set_afc_chan_sel_config <value>
hostapd_cli -i wlanx afc get_afc_chan_sel_config

where value can be 0x1 to 0x7
0x1: HOSTAPD_AFC_CHAN_SEL_CUR_PWR_LT_AFC_PWR
Trigger the AFC if its power is less than the current power
0x2: HOSTAPD_AFC_CHAN_SEL_CUR_PWR_EQ_AFC_PWR
Trigger the AFC if its power is equal to the current power
0x4: HOSTAPD_AFC_CHAN_SEL_CUR_PWR_GT_AFC_PWR
Trigger the AFC if its power is greater than the current power
0x7: HOSTAPD_AFC_CHAN_SEL_ALL
Trigger the AFC in all conditions.

Feature: AFC
